1
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:55,740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

2
00:00:56,820 --> 00:00:59,780
=Episode 23=
=Sorry, I Love You=

3
00:01:07,240 --> 00:01:08,600
Everyone's watching, huh?

4
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:10,480
Xibei.

5
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:12,520
Can you let my brother hear me?

6
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:13,640
Sure.

7
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:14,960
I'll handle the call access.

8
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:19,200
Brother.

9
00:01:20,680 --> 00:01:22,280
You said you'd always be with me.

10
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:24,680
Did you forget?

11
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:25,800
Brother.

12
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:28,440
How long is "forever", really?

13
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,480
Forever...

14
00:01:31,320 --> 00:01:32,200
It must be...

15
00:01:32,880 --> 00:01:33,800
longer than Miaomiao's

16
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:35,480
entire math workbook.

17
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:37,440
I don't believe that.

18
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:39,800
It ends after just three pages.

19
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,240
You just don't like studying.

20
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:51,320
There, look, seagulls.

21
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:52,200
Look, hurry up.

22
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,400
Where?

23
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:54,760
Right here.

24
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,720
Miaomiao, do you like seagulls?

25
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,320
Yeah, I do.

26
00:02:04,880 --> 00:02:06,280
I wish I could fly too.

27
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:09,960
Brother.

28
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,160
Will you always stay with me?

29
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,400
Of course I will.

30
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:18,840
I will always protect my Miaomiao.

31
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:21,680
You promise?

32
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,280
I promise.

33
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:30,290
Aming.

34
00:02:30,300 --> 00:02:31,150
Miaomiao.

35
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:32,400
There are seashells here.

36
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:37,200
They're huge.

37
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,120
Look, a rainbow.

38
00:02:43,880 --> 00:02:45,120
For real? Another one?

39
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:49,800
I'm not your brother!

40
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,600
He's been gone for a long time.

41
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,440
Zhou Haoran.

42
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,640
Lin Xibei.

43
00:02:58,440 --> 00:03:02,400
You two ungrateful rats.

44
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:03,920
Without me,

45
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,800
you should've been gone,

46
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,240
buried in some forgotten corner.

47
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:10,280
Why did you betray me?

48
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:14,280
Why?

49
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:16,280
Why?

50
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:18,080
Why?

51
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:25,600
Yu Kun.

52
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,340
You're having a mental split.

53
00:03:27,340 --> 00:03:28,560
Your mind's completely clouded.

54
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:30,040
Take a deep breath.

55
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:33,280
You're out of your mind.

56
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:36,520
Your whole family's nuts.

57
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,280
Yu Kun, you lowlife!

58
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:41,120
If you dare harm Ding Daang,

59
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,880
I swear I won't let you go.

60
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:44,240
Brother, calm down.

61
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,400
The police are on their way.

62
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,080
Boss, she is Ding Daang,

63
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,480
the woman you love the most.

64
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:50,360
Boss, I messed up. I'm sorry.

65
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:52,880
- Boss!
- Shut up!

66
00:03:56,620 --> 00:03:57,500
(No signal)

67
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,120
They said I have feelings for you.

68
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:14,760
Said I love you.

69
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,960
How could that be possible?

70
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,720
Then prove it to me.

71
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:49,240
If everything in the past was fake,

72
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:51,280
then end me now.

73
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:57,480
If everything in the past was a lie,

74
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,840
then end me now!

75
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,640
Aming.

76
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,480
My name is Ding Daang.

77
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:09,840
Like the sound

78
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:11,360
of a spoon falling into a bowl.

79
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,160
What if another girl shows up

80
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,480
and insists on chasing after you?

81
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:21,440
I'll just tell her
I already have a girlfriend.

82
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,360
Come back.

83
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:28,960
Chen Aming!

84
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:37,600
ظآزAnd there's that little cat
by the windowظآز

85
00:05:38,930 --> 00:05:42,190
ظآزAlways stretching relaxedظآز

86
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:44,240
Ding Daang and Chen Aming

87
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:47,180
will stay together forever.

88
00:05:47,180 --> 00:05:50,920
ظآزSometimes I dream of it
without meaning toظآز

89
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:53,280
Aming!

90
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:54,160
Chen Aming.

91
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:55,040
Aming.

92
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:04,890
ظآزTears always fall for no reasonظآز

93
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:05,800
Aming.

94
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:08,520
Chen Aming!

95
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:11,200
Wake up,
the sun's already heating your back.

96
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:13,080
Chen Aming.

97
00:06:16,680 --> 00:06:18,040
Aming.

98
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,920
Wake up.

99
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:22,200
The sun's already heating your back.

100
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:26,440
I'm almost done reading
the novel "Sugar and Lies".

101
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,440
Aming.

102
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:30,960
Do you still remember

103
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:33,360
how that novel ended?

104
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:35,000
Aming died.

105
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,560
No, Aming didn't die.

106
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:55,390
ظآزSometimes I dream of it
without meaning toظآز

107
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:56,240
Ding Daang.

108
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,680
What are you doing here?

109
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,840
You shouldn't be here.

110
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,080
Go, now!

111
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,080
Chen Aming.

112
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:06,880
Thank you.

113
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,520
Thank you for being part of my youth.

114
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:10,560
You lit up my world.

115
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,480
If I don't say it now, it'll be too late.

116
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,720
Too late? What do you mean?

117
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,600
What are you talking about?

118
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,480
Go, hurry.

119
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,000
Aming.

120
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,760
Yu Kun isn't your enemy.

121
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,880
He's the armor that shields you.

122
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:32,380
When everything feels too heavy to bear,

123
00:07:32,380 --> 00:07:34,040
he's the one who stands up
to protect you.

124
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:37,120
Chen Aming,

125
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,760
it's time you faced it all.

126
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,440
Aming,

127
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,040
be braver.

128
00:07:45,420 --> 00:07:46,500
(Sugar and Lies)

129
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:48,480
Just like the ending of this novel.

130
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,680
Ding Daang said to Chen Aming,

131
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,240
"as long as you count to three,

132
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,600
everything will be alright".

133
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,200
One.

134
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,400
No.

135
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,240
Two.

136
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,400
Three.

137
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,640
Don't!

138
00:08:21,910 --> 00:08:28,480
ظآزMaybe time will slowly
wear our edges downظآز

139
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:29,960
Move aside.

140
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:35,430
ظآزWhen we look back,
we'll just laugh at our youthظآز

141
00:08:35,680 --> 00:08:40,640
ظآزIf we could go back,
even for a secondظآز

142
00:08:40,680 --> 00:08:42,120
Let go.

143
00:08:42,900 --> 00:08:47,040
ظآزI'd give up everything
just to see your smile againظآز

144
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:48,160
It

145
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,160
is

146
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:57,840
over!

147
00:09:04,380 --> 00:09:07,140
(I owe you too much.)

148
00:09:08,170 --> 00:09:12,620
ظآزEverything in my memory
feels so beautifulظآز

149
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,080
It's over.

150
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,200
Yu Kun.

151
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,560
Look closely,

152
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:22,680
I can break free
from the cage you think I'm in.

153
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,280
So,

154
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:41,040
you plan to replace me?

155
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:43,000
Yu Kun.

156
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,560
Don't you get it yet?

157
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,280
I am you

158
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:50,720
and you are me.

159
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:54,400
Neither of us can replace the other.

160
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,200
All these years,

161
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,680
you're the one who took care

162
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:03,520
of Miaomiao
and built Keep Love from scratch.

163
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:07,290
Thank you for living the life I couldn't.

164
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,440
You won.

165
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:19,000
But so what?

166
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,640
We're both exhausted.

167
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:23,840
Aren't we?

168
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:35,840
Why?

169
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:39,400
Why not now?

170
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:43,600
I was just one step away.

171
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,480
So close, yet still short.

172
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,800
Because she's still waiting for us.

173
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:56,560
They're all waiting for us to come home.

174
00:11:06,160 --> 00:11:07,240
Have you made up your mind?

175
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:10,840
If you go back now,

176
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:13,240
those memories

177
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,080
and all that pain...

178
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:14,930
I'm not afraid.

179
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,040
This time,

180
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,120
we face it together.

181
00:11:51,290 --> 00:11:58,290
ظآزI forgot this is a movie meant for oneظآز

182
00:12:02,690 --> 00:12:10,050
ظآزSomehow you're still here,
crying with meظآز

183
00:12:14,490 --> 00:12:16,450
ظآزThey sayظآز

184
00:12:16,850 --> 00:12:25,250
ظآزLovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movieظآز

185
00:12:25,770 --> 00:12:28,730
ظآزSome endings cannot be changedظآز

186
00:12:28,970 --> 00:12:34,890
ظآزThey don't belong in sweet memoriesظآز

187
00:12:36,290 --> 00:12:41,710
ظآزI've already lost youظآز

188
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:42,600
Ding Daang,

189
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:46,520
I might have to leave for a while.

190
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:48,720
Go ahead.

191
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:50,560
I'll wait for you.

192
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:53,640
It's not a farewell forever.

193
00:12:55,160 --> 00:12:56,000
My friend.

194
00:12:57,560 --> 00:12:58,340
Everything else

195
00:12:58,340 --> 00:12:59,280
doesn't really matter.

196
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:01,040
You coming back

197
00:13:01,640 --> 00:13:02,480
is what matters most.

198
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:08,680
But...

199
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:10,080
what if he never comes back?

200
00:13:13,280 --> 00:13:14,120
Xibei.

201
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:15,840
Love means trust.

202
00:13:15,850 --> 00:13:21,330
ظآزBound for a tragic endingظآز

203
00:13:36,490 --> 00:13:38,450
ظآزThey sayظآز

204
00:13:38,850 --> 00:13:47,250
ظآزLovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movieظآز

205
00:13:47,700 --> 00:13:50,660
ظآزSome endings cannot be changedظآز

206
00:13:50,900 --> 00:13:56,820
ظآزThey don't belong in sweet memoriesظآز

207
00:13:58,220 --> 00:14:03,980
ظآزI've already lost youظآز

208
00:14:03,980 --> 00:14:09,460
ظآزThinking of it takes my breath awayظآز

209
00:14:09,740 --> 00:14:15,700
ظآزThe movie ends, so many couples aroundظآز

210
00:14:15,700 --> 00:14:20,500
ظآزYet none were ever like usظآز

211
00:14:21,580 --> 00:14:25,620
ظآزThe past will always passظآز

212
00:14:25,940 --> 00:14:33,540
ظآزIf you could still hold me tight
in your armsظآز

213
00:14:34,020 --> 00:14:37,260
ظآزI'd believe
that there are miracles in loveظآز

214
00:14:37,820 --> 00:14:43,460
ظآزI'd prove
that I'm still in love with youظآز

215
00:14:45,940 --> 00:14:49,460
ظآزI've learned how to cherish
what we hadظآز

216
00:14:49,460 --> 00:14:55,700
ظآزBut sadly, it's not youظآز

217
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:18,370
ظآزI forgot this is a movie meant for oneظآز

218
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:29,890
ظآزSomehow you're still here,
crying with meظآز
